# Streamlit UI (`app.py`, `ui/`)

## Boundaries

- **`app.py`**: orchestration only ‚Äî session state, uploads, wiring to `ui/*` and `render_service`. No merge logic that belongs in `engine.py`.
- **Never add `import streamlit` to `engine.py`** ‚Äî merge core stays headless for CLI, tests, and Power Automate.
- **Never auto-inject AI/LLM output into `ReportEngine`** ‚Äî drafts live in `ai/*` and the AI tab; apply only via explicit UI / `ai/apply_drafts.py` paths into Excel/session meta.

