### `ui/workflow_mode.py` ‚Äî public APIs

Call these from `app.py` / `ui/menubar.py`; **do not** call private `_clear_*` / `_reset_*` / `_set_workflow` from other modules.

| API | Role |
|-----|------|
| `WORKFLOW_FOLDER` / `WORKFLOW_UPLOAD` | Mode constants (`"folder"` / `"upload"`) |
| `hosted_mode_enabled()` | Shared host hides folder workflow |
| `get_workflow_mode()` / `workflow_label(mode)` | Read current mode |
| `render_workflow_picker()` / `render_workflow_banner()` / `render_workflow_hint()` | Picker UI |
| `clear_generation_session()` | Clear generated bytes/manifest (File ‚Üí **Clear generated outputs**) |
| `reset_workflow_session()` | Full workflow reset (File ‚Üí **Change workflow‚Ä¶**) |

### `ui/menubar.py` ‚Äî help pack

- **F1** / Help ‚Üí Contents opens `help/index.html` (built by `scripts/build_help.py`).
- After Help or `docs/` edits that affect the pack: run `python scripts/build_help.py` (UX / release tiers run it first).
- Menubar may invoke `build_help.py` on first Help/F1 if `help/index.html` is missing; CI/release still require an explicit build.
- File menu clear/reset must use `clear_generation_session` / `reset_workflow_session` only.

## Report tab order

1. File status chips ‚Üí **Your next steps** (`onboarding.render_next_actions_card`) ‚Äî next-steps is the authoritative rail; chips are file-load badges only
2. Pre-flight (summary; SED/DWDA; Optional AI help hidden in Simple mode when pre-flight passes ‚Äî still available on the **error** path)
3. **Generate** (primary CTA ‚Äî sticky chrome via `.ev-sticky-cta`; not buried under appendices)
4. Appendices (collapsed in Simple mode; expander title **Appendices (optional PDF uploads)**; OneStop B/C/E/F/H with shared status badges)
5. Download ‚Äî **Download deliverable package (.zip)** as primary CTA
6. **Advanced** expander ‚Äî preview, template analysis, glossary
7. **Help & documentation** expander ‚Äî consultant doc links (collapsed)

Above the Report tab: **context strip** (workflow ‚Ä∫ profile ‚Ä∫ files) + CSS **workflow stepper** (Inputs ‚Üí Pre-flight ‚Üí Generate ‚Üí Download). Magenta is brand/CTA only; moss / amber / terracotta badges are semantic (pass / review / fail).

## Tabs

- **Report** tab ‚Äî flow above.
- Folder workflow: **AI drafts & tools** ¬∑ Upload workflow: **AI tools** (`ui/ai_panel.py`).
- AI drafts do not auto-merge unless the user applies them to Excel / sidebar override.

## Batch mode

When `ProjectData` has more than one data row, the Generate card offers **Generation mode**: **Single site** vs **All N sites (batch zip)** (plus a site row picker in single-site mode). Batch calls **`render_service.render_batch_reports()`** and stores results in `session_state.generated_batch` for **`render_batch_deliverable_success`**. Same uploaded appendices apply to every row (per-row appendices not yet supported ‚Äî see docs backlog).

## UX rules

- On launch, users **choose a workflow** (`ui/workflow_mode.py`); dismissible **Welcome** card on first use.
- **Simple mode** (default for new users) ‚Äî hides executive summary override; AI under **Advanced ‚Äî AI options**.
- **Load Alberta Phase I sample** ‚Äî sidebar button ‚Üí `session_excel_bytes` / `session_template_bytes` via `ui/helpers.py`.
- **One primary download** ‚Äî deliverable zip; `.docx` / manifest in **Advanced downloads** (`Download report (.docx)`; batch: `Download reports only (.docx zip, N files)`).
- Do **not** duplicate next-action lists in preflight ‚Äî only the Report tab **Your next steps** card.
- Persist **generated bytes and manifest** in **session state** so download survives reruns.
- **Widget session keys** ‚Äî never assign `st.session_state.<widget_key>` after that widget is drawn. Use pending keys before render.
- Surface **user-safe** errors from `security.user_safe_error`.
- Preflight cache key includes appendix label tuple; engine cache keys on Excel + template + Ecoventure workbook digest (appendices do not affect `ReportEngine` construction).
